{"head":{"title":"Emmet","category":"Markup","layout":"2017/sheet","prism_languages":["html","css"],"updated":"2020-07-03T00:00:00.000Z","intro":"Emmet is a markup language for expanding CSS rules into HTML\n"},"body":[{"title":"Child: >","elms":"\n```css\nnav>ul>li\n```\nExpands to\n```html\n<nav>\n  <ul>\n    <li></li>\n  </ul>\n</nav>\n```\n\n","h2":null},{"title":"Sibling: +","elms":"\n```css\nsection>p+p+p\n```\nExpands to\n```html\n<section>\n  <p></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p></p>\n</section>\n```\n","h2":null},{"title":"Climb Up: ^","elms":"\n```css\nsection>header>h1^footer\n```\nExpands to\n```html\n<section>\n  <header>\n    <h1></h1>\n  </header>\n  <footer></footer>\n</section>\n```\n","h2":null},{"title":"Grouping: ()","elms":"\n```css\nsection>(header>nav>ul>li)+footer>p\n```\nExpands to\n```html\n<section>\n  <header>\n    <nav>\n      <ul>\n        <li></li>\n      </ul>\n    </nav>\n  </header>\n  <footer>\n    <p></p>\n  </footer>\n</section>\n```\n","h2":null},{"title":"Multiplication: \\*","elms":"\n```css\nul>li*3\n```\nExpands to\n```html\n<ul>\n  <li></li>\n  <li></li>\n  <li></li>\n</ul>\n```\n","h2":null},{"title":"IDs and Classes: . #","elms":"\n```css\nul.menu>li.menu__item+li#id_item+li.menu__item#id_2\n```\nExpands to\n```html\n<ul class=\"menu\">\n  <li class=\"menu__item\"></li>\n  <li id=\"id_item\"></li>\n  <li class=\"menu__item\" id=\"id_2\"></li>\n</ul>\n```\n","h2":null},{"title":"Numbering: $","elms":"\n```css\nul>li.item$*3\nul>li.item$$*3\nul>li.item$@-*3\nul>li.item$@3*5\n```\nExpands to\n```html\n<ul>\n  <li class=\"item1\"></li>\n  <li class=\"item2\"></li>\n  <li class=\"item3\"></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n  <li class=\"item01\"></li>\n  <li class=\"item02\"></li>\n  <li class=\"item03\"></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n  <li class=\"item3\"></li>\n  <li class=\"item2\"></li>\n  <li class=\"item1\"></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n  <li class=\"item3\"></li>\n  <li class=\"item4\"></li>\n  <li class=\"item5\"></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n  <li class=\"item3\"></li>\n  <li class=\"item4\"></li>\n  <li class=\"item5\"></li>\n  <li class=\"item6\"></li>\n  <li class=\"item7\"></li>\n</ul>\n```\n","h2":null},{"title":"Attributes: []","elms":"\n```css\ninput[type=\"text\"]\ndiv[data-attr=\"test\"]\n```\nExpands to\n```html\n<input type=\"text\" />\n<div data-attr=\"test\"></div>\n```\n","h2":null},{"title":"Text: {}","elms":"\n```css\np{Lorem ipsum}\n```\nExpands to\n```html\n<p>Lorem ipsum</p>\n```\n","h2":null},{"title":"Implicit tags","elms":"\n```css\n.default-block\nem>.default-inline\nul>.default-list\ntable>.default-table-row>.default-table-column\n```\nExpands to\n```html\n<div class=\"default-block\"></div>\n<em><span class=\"default-inline\"></span></em>\n<ul>\n  <li class=\"default-list\"></li>\n</ul>\n<table>\n  <tr class=\"default-table-row\">\n    <td class=\"default-table-column\"></td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n```","h2":null}]}